Class FileDownloadCallable

  • java.lang.Object
    • vstore.framework.communication.download.threads.FileDownloadCallable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.concurrent.Callable<VStoreFile>

    public class FileDownloadCallable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Callable<VStoreFile>
    A simple callable for handling the download of a file. Does nothing but downloading the file from the given storage node.
